img2youtube
-----------------------------------

Get full control over the first image on the video.

This jQuery plugin turns an image into a YouTube video when you click on it.

Features:
- Progressive enhancement. If JavaScript isn't enabled the image will link to the YouTube page. If flash isn't available, HTML5 <video> is used.
- Auto-play video on click (only works if flash is installed)

Known issues:
- Auto-play doesn't work if flash isn't enabled
 